\v 6 Wherefore my fury and mine anger was poured forth, and was kindled in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem; and they are wasted \add and\add* desolate, as \add at\add* this day. 
\v 7 Therefore now thus saith the \sc Lord\sc*, the God of hosts, the God of Israel; Wherefore commit ye \add this\add* great evil against your souls, to cut off from you man and woman, child and suckling, out of Judah, to leave you none to remain; 
